{"title":"美丽的白莲","authors":["晏明"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽的白莲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晏明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久远的呼唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百年的呼唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百年的期盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百年沉重的眷恋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百年离散的澳门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"度过四百年痛苦思念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵美丽的白莲飘来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑着，笑着，飘来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧蓝蓝的海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧蓝蓝的天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澳门，一片碧蓝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，一片碧蓝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦的泪水淌满腮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来串串白莲盛开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百年的苦苦思念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时化为彩霞璀璨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百年，四百年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽开最美的欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美的欢笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是归来的白莲……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}